<P>
NATION IN BRIEF; WASHINGTON STATE; KILLER CALLED TOO HEAVY TO BE HANGED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Staff and Wire Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
