<P>
 Promotes improved human relations, civic peace and the full acceptance of all 
people in community life. The commission seeks to bring together business, 
governmental, religious, professional and other groups in order to resolve 
human relations problems. 
</P>
<P>
 Services: 
</P>
<P>
