academic decathlon team in a few years," said Councilman Randy Bressette, 
referring to the local academic team that has won state and national honors in 
recent year. 
</P>
<P>
 One of the projects that won an award for the team was a statistical survey of 
upper-grade students, which was turned into a report that was judged at the 
competition. 
</P>
<P>
 "We are very proud of our fourth-grade math team," said Janice Mecham, a 
Valencia teacher who coached the fourth-graders. "They spent many hours 
preparing for the tournament." FRANK MESSINA 
