<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Clarification -- In a May 9 article on the Los Angeles Philharmonic, 
trombonist Ralph Sauer said that he was leaving the orchestra at the end of the 
season "to pursue other interests." Ernest Fleischmann, the orchestra's 
executive vice president and managing director, has said that his subsequent 
quote did not apply to Sauer or any other specific individual. 
</P>
